<p class=" " style="text-indent: -18pt; line-height: normal; background: white;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol; color: rgb(68, 68, 68);"><span>·<span style="font: 7pt "Times New Roman";">&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;
</span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Roboto, serif; color: rgb(68, 68, 68);">&#xa0; Поощрение и
